This paper deals with the convergence rate of a system of agents, which is a common topic in the field of multi-agent systems (MAS). Therefore, cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the study of dynamics and convergence, which are topics in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also deals with systems and control, which are topics in cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
